# - Try to find LLVM
# Once done this will define
#
#  LLVM_FOUND - system has LLVM
#  LLVM_INCLUDE_DIRS - the LLVM include directory
#  LLVM_LIBRARIES - Link these to use LLVM
#  LLVM_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using LLVM
